1. *Svuda* se vidi da je zima (Everywhere it can be seen that it's winter).
2. On je bio *svuda* poznat (He was known everywhere).
3. *Svud* se čuje da je veliki grad (It is heard everywhere that it is a big city).
4. *Svuda* se tragaju prava istina (Truths are sought everywhere).
5. *Svud* se zna da je lako krasti (It is known everywhere that it is easy to steal).